<sentence type="quasi">３級の実務経験年数（実務経験のみの場合）を<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t42" type="DURATION" value="P1Y" valueFromSurface="P1Y">１年</TIMEX3>から<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t43" type="DURATION" value="P6M" valueFromSurface="P6M">６月</TIMEX3>に短縮</sentence>
